library(ciatej2024)

Use the browse* functions to explore the documentation of the magrittr, dplyr, and tidyr packages:

browse_magrittr()
#> [1] "index.html"     "magrittr.html"  "tradeoffs.html"
browse_dplyr()
#>  [1] "base.html"             "colwise.html"          "dplyr.html"           
#>  [4] "grouping.html"         "in-packages.html"      "index.html"           
#>  [7] "programming.html"      "rowwise.html"          "two-table.html"       
#> [10] "window-functions.html"
browse_tidyr()

#> [5] "programming.html" "rectangle.html"   "tidy-data.html"
